@node "plans" "--------[ HISTORY/FUTURE ]--------"
@next "reg"
@prev "bugs"
@{b}@{u} History: @{ub}@{uu}

 - v1.0 (96-04-03) first public release

 - v1.1 (96-04-16) - fixed CR/LF bug in LogonManagerSetup   

                   - using the doors-priority from BBSConfig-settings

                   - added seperate values for Topaz/IBM logo size

                   - using 'Print Line' instead of 'Tilde Print Line'
                     for displaying the labels (more secure with wrong 
                     config-files)

                   - using the doors-path                     

@{b}@{u} TODO: @{ub}@{uu}
 
 - more options
 
 - scrolling if the entries don't fit on one screen
 
 - delete the created @{i}@{fg fill}Text-Welcome##..@{ui}@{fg text} files
   (does anyone have a good idea how to accomplish this?)
 
 ...
 

                             @{" back to main menu " link "main" 0}
@endnode

